TITLE: Using PhysicsHelper for Complex Force Effects in Babylon.js
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the PhysicsHelper utility to create various force phenomena including radial explosions, gravitational fields, updrafts, and vortices. Each method accepts parameters for origin, radius, strength, and additional effect-specific options.
