TITLE: Creating Heightmap From Square Ribbon in Babylon.js
DESCRIPTION: This code generates a heightmap from a square ribbon using mathematical functions to create paths. The snippet defines an exponential path function, creates an array of paths, and then builds a ribbon mesh with a HeightmapImpostor for physics interactions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babylonjs/documentation/blob/master/content/features/featuresDeepDive/physics/v1/advancedPhysicsFeatures.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

