SOURCE: https://github.com/babylonjs/documentation/blob/master/content/features/featuresDeepDive/mesh/highlightLayer.md#2025-04-23_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// Add the highlight layer.
const hl2 = new BABYLON.HighlightLayer("hl2", scene);
hl2.addMesh(ground, BABYLON.Color3.Red());

const alpha = 0;
scene.registerBeforeRender(() => {
  alpha += 0.06;

  hl2.blurHorizontalSize = 0.3 + Math.cos(alpha) * 0.6 + 0.6;
