TITLE: Calculating Inward Direction Vector
DESCRIPTION: Computes a random inward-pointing vector using facet normal, tangent, and binormal vectors
SOURCE: https://github.com/babylonjs/documentation/blob/master/content/toolsAndResources/utilities/InnerMeshPoints.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
