TITLE: Handling Skeleton Animations with LayerMask in Babylon.js
DESCRIPTION: Implementation showing how to update skeleton animations when using layerMasks with multiple cameras. This solution ensures animated meshes remain properly animated even when hidden from the active camera by preparing the skeleton before each frame rendering.
