TITLE: Creating a KTX2 Decoder Web Worker (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Defines a web worker script (`worker.js`) for decoding KTX2 textures off the main thread. It imports the KTX2 decoder module, the core worker function, the MSC transcoder WASM JavaScript module, sets up necessary global variables, configures the MSC transcoder, and invokes the main worker function.
