TITLE: Private Camera Follow Method
DESCRIPTION: Private method to update camera position to follow a target using spherical coordinates.
SOURCE: https://github.com/babylonjs/documentation/blob/master/content/contribute/toBabylon/contributeToAPI.md#2025-04-23_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
private follow(): void {
    if (!this.target) {
        return;
    }
    this._cartesianCoordinates.x = this.radius * Math.cos(this.alpha) * Math.cos(this.beta);
    this._cartesianCoordinates.y = this.radius * Math.sin(this.beta);
    this._cartesianCoordinates.z = this.radius * Math.sin(this.alpha) * Math.cos(this.beta);

    const targetPosition = this.target.getAbsolutePosition();
    this.position = targetPosition.add(this._cartesianCoordinates);
    this.setTarget(targetPosition);
}
```

